      <title>中国央行停止为期 18 个月的黄金购买狂潮，黄金价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/china-s-pboc-halts-gold-purchases-after-price-hits-record-in-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行上个月没有购买任何黄金，结束了持续 18 个月的大规模购买狂潮，并推动黄金价格在 5 月份创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/china-s-pboc-halts-gold-purchases-after-price-hits-record-in-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:06:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
